criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion criteria:

        The inclusion criteria for the two groups (experimental and Sham) in the research will be:

          -  Subjects of both sexes over 18 years of age;

          -  Subjects with pain in the trapezius muscle in the last three months without definite
             cause; Obs: They should present at least "moderate" pain in NDI sessions 1 and 3 in
             the subjective pain reported in VAS.

        Exclusion Criteria:

        The exclusion criteria for both groups will be:

          -  Neurological diseases;

          -  History of trauma or cervical spine surgeries;

          -  Clinical diagnosis of hernia or nerve compression;

          -  Previous physiotherapy (last three months).
